description: Harbor是一个用于存储和分发Docker镜像的企业级Registry服务器，通过添加一些企业必需的功能特性，例如安全、标识和管理等，扩展了开源Docker Distribution。
description_en: Harbor is an enterprise-level Registry server for storing and distributing Docker images, extending the open source Docker Distribution by adding some of the business-required features such as security, identity, and management.
